Title: Web Forms MVP
Description:
A simple Model-View-Presenter framework for ASP.NET Web Forms to aid in building testable and maintainable ASP.NET projects. Features support for normal server controls, data-binding and async pages.

Requires ASP.NET 3.5 SP1
TagList: ASP.NET,ASP.NET 3.5 SP1,MVP,Model View Presenter,Model-View-Presenter,Test Driven Design,Testing,R&D,CMS,ASP.NET 4.0,
